basics.name: Ethan Morrell
basics.label: Undergraduate Student
basics.summary: Hi, I'm Ethan! I am studying for a B.A. in Information and Computer Sciences with a concentration in Security Science at the University of Hawaii at Manoa. I expect to graduate in Spring, 2026.

courses: ICS 111: Introduction to Computer Science I (Object-Oriented Programming)
ICS 211: Introduction to Computer Science II (Data Structures)
ICS 141: Discrete Mathematics for Computer Science I
ICS 241: Discrete Mathematics for Computer Science II
ICS 222: Basic Concepts of Computer Science

highlights: Delivered weekly Python programming lessons to ~20 middle school students
Helped students develop personal projects for their final presentations
